uzo \\\"Le Parrain\\\" et dans le film Le Parrain, r\\u00e9alis\\u00e9 par Francis Ford Coppola en 1972. Il est le chef et parrain de la famille Corleone, l\\u2019une des plus puissantes mafia des \\u00c9tats-Unis.<\\/p>\\n<p>Il a cinq enfants .<\\/p>\\n<p>Vito Corleone a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 d\\u00e9crit comme \\u00e9tant proche de nombreuses figures historiques r\\u00e9elles. Le magazine Premi\\u00e8re a d\\u00e9sign\\u00e9 Vito Corleone comme \\u00e9tant le plus grand personnage de l\'histoire du cin\\u00e9ma .<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a437b85\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1dded3c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"383914d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":169,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b2fff6f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1b0bc32\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4900fbb\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/01\\/Al_Pacino_-_Hummel.jpg\",\"id\":95,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2085e91\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"content_position\":\"center\",\"space_between_widgets\":1},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"efa33ed\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/01\\/michael_corleone.jpg\",\"id\":89,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100,\"sizes\":[]},\"space\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100,\"sizes\":[]},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"